                     <interp inst="t18261207-241-off1402" type="offenceSubcategory" value="housebreaking"></interp>
               breaking and entering the dwelling-house of 
                     <persName id="t18261207-241-victim1350" type="victimName">
                        George 
                        Deane, the younger<interp inst="t18261207-241-victim1350" type="surname" value="Deane"></interp>
